Package com.guppy.visualiserweb.data.model

Class EdgeData

java.lang.Object
com.guppy.visualiserweb.data.model.EdgeData
public class EdgeData extends Object
Represents the data associated with an edge in a graph. Contains properties such as ID, weight, source, and target nodes.
Author:
HegdeSagar
